              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">API Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">RESTful and GraphQL API design and development. API gateway implementation and documentation.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ REST & GraphQL APIs</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ API gateway setup</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Developer portals</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-secondary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M5.5 16a3.5 3.5 0 01-.369-6.98 4 4 0 117.753-1.977A4.5 4.5 0 1113.5 16h-8z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cloud Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Scalable, resilient cloud architecture on AWS, Azure, or GCP. Microservices and serverless design.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Microservices architecture</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Serverless solutions</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Auto-scaling design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 2a1 1 0 011 1v2.101a7.002 7.002 0 0111.601 2.566 1 1 0 11-1.885.666A5.002 5.002 0 005.999 7H9a1 1 0 010 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V3a1 1 0 011-1zm.008 9.057a1 1 0 011.276.61A5.002 5.002 0 0014.001 13H11a1 1 0 110-2h5a1 1 0 011 1v5a1 1 0 11-2 0v-2.101a7.002 7.002 0 01-11.601-2.566 1 1 0 01.61-1.276z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">DevOps & CI/CD</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Automated deployment pipelines, infrastructure as code, and continuous delivery practices.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ CI/CD pipelines</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Infrastructure as code</li>
