          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Platform Engineering</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Internal developer platforms, tooling, and self-service infrastructure for engineering teams.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Developer experience</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Self-service portals</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Golden paths</li>
            </ul>
